comments: Graham (CHA) brushes Fournier's (ORL) side during the pick.
Anthony (ORL) maintains a legal defensive position alongside Graham (CHA) and absorbs the contact as Graham takes a step towards Anthony at the end of the drive.
Anthony (ORL) legally contests Graham's (CHA) driving shot attempt.
Biyombo (CHA) makes marginal contact with Fournier's (ORL) body on the gather and maintains a legal defensive position as Fournier continues his driving shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) engages and disengages with Washington (CHA) during the rebound.
Hayward (CHA) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Anthony's (ORL) path and does not deliver any contact.
Anthony (ORL) legally contests Hayward's (CHA) jump shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) legally firms up in Graham's (CHA) path and does not deliver any contact during the pick.
Washington (CHA) legally firms up in Anthony's (ORL) path and does not deliver any contact during the pick.
Ross (ORL) legally contests Rozier's (CHA) jump shot attempt.
As Hayward (CHA) spins, his off-arm briefly makes contact with Anthony's (ORL) arm. The contact is marginal and he immediately slide his arm off of Anthony.
Anthony (ORL) reaches in and makes contact with the ball, followed by marginal contact with Hayward's (CHA) arm.
Ross (ORL) makes marginal contact with Biyombo (CHA) during the rebound.
Vucevic (ORL) commits a take foul on Biyombo (CHA).
Fournier (ORL) places his off-arm against Rozier (CHA) and the contact is marginal as he releases during the drive.
Hayward (CHA) legally contests Ross' (ORL) jump shot attempt.
Washington (CHA) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Fournier's (ORL) path and does not deliver any contact.
Prior to Hayward completing his driving shot attempt at the basket, Fournier (ORL) makes marginal contact with Hayward's (CHA) backside on the gather.
ORL fails to inbound the ball within five seconds.
Bacon (ORL) briefly grasps Hayward's (CHA) arm.
Bacon (ORL) commits a take foul on Hayward (CHA).
